      "message": "In addition, there is no need to clear the button reference here. Don\u0027t confuse \"disposing\" method with \"dispose\" method. \"disposing\" is a callback that fires when the *dispatcher* is destructed. \"dispose\" is a method where you clean anything when *your class* is due to be destructed. (And since you simply do clear() on it in Button::dispose, there is no need to manually clear the button reference inside it.)",
